pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Idzi data rinoratidzwa padashibhodhi rino rinounganidzwa zvakananga kubva mumhinduro dzeongororo uye haribvi pahuwandu hwenyika kana seti dzedata. Inomiririra pfungwa dzakataurwa nevechidiki panguva yeongororo, uye chero mhedziso dzakatorwa kubva mumhinduro idzi ibasa remushandisi, kwete PMNCH. PMNCH yakazvipira kuremekedza, kusimudzira nekuchengetedza kodzero nekugara zvakanaka kwevanhu vese. Maonero api neapi anoratidzwa mumhinduro dzeongororo kana zvinyorwa zvakatsikiswa zvinobuda mudhishibhodhi inopikisana nekuzvipira uku hazvitsigirwe nePMNCH.

wra03a-subtext: Wana mukana wemhinduro dzakavhurika dzinosvika miriyoni imwe nemazana maviri kuburikidza neiyi dashibhodhi inodyidzana, chishandiso chakasiyana chinobatanidza manzwi evakadzi nevasikana nemikana isingaperi yekuongorora dhijitari.
pmn01a-subtext: Kugamuchirwa ku“Zvinodiwa Nevechiduku” Dashboard! Ichi chishandiso chinopindirana chinopa mufananidzo unooneka wemhinduro uye maonero atiri kuunganidza kubva kune vechidiki vane makore 10-24 pasi rose. Nheyo yechirongwa ichi mubvunzo wakazaruka: "Kuti ndivandudze hupenyu hwangu, ndinoda ...". Vechidiki kubva pasi rose vanga vachipindura izvi, vachitipa maonero akasiyana mune zvavanoda, tariro, uye zvishuvo zvavo. Ongorora iyo data, tsvaga nyaya dziri kumashure kwenhamba, uye ubatane nesu mukukudza manzwi evadiki bhiriyoni 1.8 pasi rese. Kuti udzidze zvakawanda nezvemushandirapamwe, shanya http://www.1point8.org.
